Inga Kolegova, the Head of the State Environmental Service, invoking her candidacy to the position of the Director General of the State Revenue Service (SRS), has saved the government from the fall, according to Ojārs Skudra, Associate Professor of the Faculty of Social Sciences of the University of Latvia.
